      • createStoragePool

        String createStoragePool(RestParams params,
                         AddStoragePool storagePoolDto,
                         boolean useJsonRequest)
        The module aids in creation of storage pool when provided with the storage pool details as an AddStoragePool object or JsonRequest.
        Parameters:
        params - The RestParams is a structure containing the connection details.
        storagePoolDto - Object containing the storage pool details, used to create a storage pool.
        useJsonRequest - The JsonRequest body is part of AddStoragePool object which takes in a String containing the new storage pool details, which is converted to AddStoragePool object using adaptor and processed.
        Returns:
        String Created if successful.

      • updateStoragePool

        String updateStoragePool(RestParams params,
                         String resourceId,
                         StoragePool storagePoolDto,
                         boolean useJsonRequest)
        This module aids in refreshing the storage pool. To request a refresh of a storage pool, the user must set the "refreshState" attribute to RefreshState.RefreshPending state.
        Parameters:
        params - The RestParams is a structure containing the connection details.
        resourceId - The resource identifier for storage pool as seen in HPE OneView.
        storagePoolDto - Object containing the storage pool details, used to update a storage pool.
        useJsonRequest - The JsonRequest body is part of StoragePool object which takes in a String containing the update to be made, which is converted to StoragePool object using an adaptor and processed.
        Returns:
        String, is Updated if successful.

      • deleteStoragePool

        String deleteStoragePool(RestParams params,

        The module aids in deleting a storage pool for the specified storage pool resource identifier.
        Parameters:
        params - The RestParams is a structure containing the connection details.
        resourceId - The resource identifier for storage pool as seen in HPE OneView.
        Returns:
        String Deleted if successful.

      • getId

        String getId(RestParams params,
             String name,
             String storageSystemUri)
        The module aids in fetching the storage pool resource identifier for the storage pool name as specified in HPE OneView.
        Parameters:
        params - The RestParams is a structure containing the connection details.
        name - The resourceName is the storage pool name as seen in HPE OneView.
        storageSystemUri - The uri of the storage system the storage pool is associated with.
        Returns:
        String which is the resource identifier for the storage pool name as seen in HPE OneView.
